Properties.Caption: Просмотр банковских выписок со счета 40101
Properties.Tag: Select [K_TD].[CTD] As [Тип документа], Max([K_TD].[NTD]) As [Наименование типа документа], [BNV_LINES].[CDOC] As [Номер платежного документа], [BNV_LINES].[PBK] As [ПБК строки выписки], [BNV_LINES].[INN] As [ИНН Плательщика выписка], [BNV_LINES].[DATE] As [Дата], Case When [BNV_LINES].[DT_CT]=1 Then 'Д' Else 'К' End As [ДК], Sum([BNV_LINES].[SUMM]) As [Сумма], Max([BNV_LINES].[NPL]) As [Назначение платежа документа] From ((([BNV_LINES] With (NoLock) Inner Join [DOC_DO] With (NoLock) On ([BNV_LINES].[DOCID]=[DOC_DO].[DOCID])) Inner Join [K_TD] With (NoLock) On ([BNV_LINES].[K_TDID]=[K_TD].[K_TDID])) Left Join [IMPORT_MERDOK] With (NoLock) On ([BNV_LINES].[GUID]=[IMPORT_MERDOK].[ELNUM] And [BNV_LINES].[K_TSID]=[IMPORT_MERDOK].[K_TSID])) Where [BNV_LINES].[K_TDID] In (27,35) And |0 Group by [K_TD].[CTD], [BNV_LINES].[CDOC], [BNV_LINES].[PBK], [BNV_LINES].[INN], [BNV_LINES].[DATE], Case When [BNV_LINES].[DT_CT]=1 Then 'Д' Else 'К' End Order by |1
Properties.Name: Просмотр банковских выписок со счета 40101
